# Common Interview Mistakes

❌ Forgetting `break`

```java
case 1:
    System.out.println("One");
```

May cause fall-through.

---

❌ Using switch for ranges

```java
switch(marks >= 40)
```

Wrong.

Use `if-else`.

---

❌ Omitting the default case

Always include a default block to handle unexpected values.

